entry.title: Introduction to the site
entry.content: Hello peoples around the world, this is my first blog on this new site of mine. I will be adding updates on what I’m doing and some news and stuff like that. This is actually not the actual site, my other site is a WIP and it won’t be out yet in quiet some time, and when that time comes Ill leave a link in one of my other blogs, but no need to get all excited and expect to come in couple days, it’ll come in more like a couple months, so yeah. If any of you happen to see this, you might want to check this out https://srcratch.mit.edu/users/Thecomediancanadian and also click the boxes on this page. If you don’t have an account on this I highly recommend for you to get an account and get started!!
